headline: Next-generation HPE Cray Supercomputing portfolio introduces industry-leading compute density to boost AI productivity

headline: HPE to Present Live Audio Webcast of Fiscal 2025 Fourth Quarter Earnings Conference Call
summary: HOUSTON, November 13, 2025--HPE (NYSE: HPE) will conduct a live audio webcast of a conference call with analysts to review financial results for the fourth quarter of fiscal 2025, which ended October 31, 2025.

headline: Cisco Shares Surge After AI-Fueled Outlook Exceeds Estimates
summary: Cisco also increased its earnings forecast, which similarly topped analysts’ predictions.  The outlook sparked fresh optimism that Cisco can benefit from booming AI spending.  Demand for Cisco’s technology highlights the need for secure networking “as customers move quickly to unlock the potential of AI,” Chief Executive Officer Chuck Robbins said in a statement.
